12
00:01:32,650 --> 00:01:34,729
<i>Not normal men, for sure.</i>

13
00:01:34,730 --> 00:01:38,974
<i>Rebels, lunatics, dreamers.</i>

14
00:01:39,650 --> 00:01:42,051
<i>People who are desperate to make a mark</i>

15
00:01:42,170 --> 00:01:44,411
<i>and are prepared to die trying.</i>

16
00:01:46,490 --> 00:01:47,855
<i>My name is Niki Lauda,</i>

17
00:01:48,210 --> 00:01:51,409
<i>and racing people
know me for two things.</i>

18
00:01:51,410 --> 00:01:55,176
<i>The first is my rivalry with him.</i>

19
00:01:57,537 --> 00:01:59,077
<i>You want to change?</i>

20
00:01:59,330 --> 00:02:02,254
<i>Photographers,
please clear the grid.</i>

21
00:02:02,770 --> 00:02:04,738
What about Hunt? Has he changed?

22
00:02:05,010 --> 00:02:06,529
No, he's going on wets.

23
00:02:06,530 --> 00:02:09,729
<i>I don't know
why it became such a big thing.</i>

24
00:02:09,730 --> 00:02:13,098
<i>We were just drivers
busting each other's balls.</i>

25
00:02:14,090 --> 00:02:16,609
<i>To me this is perfectly normal,</i>

26
00:02:16,610 --> 00:02:18,849
<i>but other people saw it differently,</i>

27
00:02:18,850 --> 00:02:21,774
<i>that whatever it was between us
went deeper.</i>

28
00:02:23,130 --> 00:02:26,213
Then we go on wets too.

29
00:02:38,050 --> 00:02:40,129
<i>The other thing I'm remembered for</i>

30
00:02:40,130 --> 00:02:43,969
<i>is what happened on 1st August, 1976,</i>

31
00:02:43,970 --> 00:02:45,569
<i>when I was chasing him</i>

32
00:02:45,570 --> 00:02:47,729
<i>like an asshole.</i>

33
00:03:18,170 --> 00:03:19,689
Trauma trolley, please.

34
00:03:19,690 --> 00:03:22,169
Hello, I think the racetrack
telephoned ahead that I was coming.

35
00:03:22,170 --> 00:03:23,615
Hunt. James Hunt.

36
00:03:28,690 --> 00:03:31,773
What's the matter? No one ever seen
a spot of blood before?

37
00:03:32,130 --> 00:03:34,781
- Are you all right?
- Absolutely fine.

38
00:03:37,930 --> 00:03:39,819
We all thought
you'd been in an accident.

39
00:03:39,930 --> 00:03:40,977
I have.

40
00:03:41,130 --> 00:03:44,293
If you call a friendly disagreement
with another driver an accident.

41
00:03:50,450 --> 00:03:52,289
What did you disagree about?

42
00:03:52,290 --> 00:03:53,860
It's none of your business.

43
00:03:53,970 --> 00:03:55,972
Sorry.

44
00:03:56,970 --> 00:03:58,335
His wife.

45
