It was a nasty blow.
Done with a bloody crowbar.

47
00:04:06,970 --> 00:04:09,735
- Why? What did you do?
- Nothing.

48
00:04:10,330 --> 00:04:12,571
Only what she asked me to do.

49
00:04:14,810 --> 00:04:16,335
Which was...

50
00:04:16,970 --> 00:04:19,496
I'd be happy to show you, if you like.

51
00:04:22,690 --> 00:04:24,977
Oh! Sorry.

52
00:04:25,090 --> 00:04:28,890
<i>I have a theory
why women like racing drivers.</i>

53
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:31,649
<i>It's not because
they respect what we do,</i>

54
00:04:31,650 --> 00:04:34,529
<i>driving round and round in circles.</i>

55
00:04:34,530 --> 00:04:37,101
<i>Mostly they think that's pathetic,
and they're probably right.</i>

56
00:04:38,330 --> 00:04:40,412
<i>It's our closeness to death.</i>

57
00:04:41,250 --> 00:04:45,009
<i>You see, the closer you are to death,
the more alive you feel.</i>

58
00:04:45,010 --> 00:04:48,089
<i>The more alive you are.
